snippet.title: Bayonetta & Vanquish 10th Anniversary Bundle | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Ten years after their original debut, Bayonetta and Sam Gideon return in the Bayonetta & Vanquish 10th Anniversary Bundle on PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on February 18, 2020!

Pre-order the SteelBook bundle today featuring new cover art for both games:

http://bit.ly/BayoVanq
